data.description: Check out this 3 bedroom charmer sitting on a quiet lot in Sadorus! You'll find a spacious dining room featuring a gorgeous beadboard ceiling and updated low-maintenance flooring. Just off the dining room, the kitchen offers great cabinet space. Head through the French glass doors to find the bright and airy living room with new carpet. The three ample sized bedrooms each boast new flooring and share the full bathroom. Enjoy the fresh fall air out in the covered porch overlooking the large yard. Take a look at this one today!
